Coffee is a worldwide drink, been part of any culture.

 There are some concerns about effects of coffee on the health.

 Recently, epidemiological studies have shown benefits of coffee drinking to diabetics and also to prevent diabetes in populations.

 We aim to understand some effects of coffee and not only caffeine over vascular system, in special coronary artery disease patients, diabetics end normal people.

